### Database API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:3333/:dbType
### Replace :dbType with 'pg' for PostgreSQL or 'mysql' for MySQL

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333/pg

### ============================================
### GET /databases - List all databases
### Returns list of all databases on the server
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/databases
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### GET /databases/current - Get current database
### Returns the name of the currently connected database
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/databases/current
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### GET /databases/connection - Get connection info
### Returns connection details and server information
### (PostgreSQL version, host, port, user, current database, connection counts)
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/databases/connection
Content-Type: application/json
